message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $120. I believe it's a great deal for the value it provides.
Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I can only pay up to $95. Let me know if this works for you.
Hi Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $120 is the lowest I can go. This product is in high demand and I'm confident in its value.
